snippet.title: My Candy Love: Love Life | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover a new adventure in this third opus of My Candy Love!
 
University is over, and a bright future lays ahead of you. With your diploma in hand, you head towards the unknown in the company of the person you cherish the most.
For the past three years, you’ve been fulfilled in your profession as well as in your relationship.
But work isn’t always easy, and love also has its challenges...
